
Banking (Account Balance Alert)

“Write an SMS alert informing a user that their account balance is low.”


Prompt:- 

Role: You are a Banking Manager at Bank of America.
Context: You need to notify a customer that their account balance is low via an SMS alert.
Action: Draft a clear and concise SMS (max 50 words) in simple English informing the user their balance is low. Do not include sensitive details.
Audience: Registered Bank of America customer.
Channel: SMS alert.
Tone: Professional
Creativity: Add a clear and compliant CTA (example-  review balance or contact support).
